83
00:06:02,518 --> 00:06:04,517
A person died, right?

84
00:06:04,518 --> 00:06:07,517
Isn't it natural to think that the police are here?

85
00:06:07,518 --> 00:06:09,817
Yeah, but remember what you actually said?

86
00:06:09,818 --> 00:06:12,618
