95
00:06:35,718 --> 00:06:38,717
Fair enough, next question then!

96
00:06:38,718 --> 00:06:42,417
It's been a while since we got here.

97
00:06:42,418 --> 00:06:46,018
But why are you not getting mad at us?

98
00:06:52,118 --> 00:06:53,817
