101
00:06:59,918 --> 00:07:02,017
A normal person would say,

102
00:07:02,018 --> 00:07:06,217
"Who the heck are those kids?"

103
00:07:06,218 --> 00:07:07,717
Oh, that...

104
00:07:07,718 --> 00:07:10,217
You didn't say anything,

105
00:07:10,218 --> 00:07:13,317
