106
00:07:13,318 --> 00:07:18,518
You knew that we were important witnesses of the jewel robbery.

107
00:07:24,718 --> 00:07:26,417
Is that true?

108
00:07:26,418 --> 00:07:27,917
-No. -Wait a minute.

109
00:07:27,918 --> 00:07:29,817
