112
00:07:37,119 --> 00:07:39,817
"Put the jewels in this bag!" -The jewel robber!

113
00:07:39,818 --> 00:07:42,017
It was you, wasn't it?

114
00:07:42,018 --> 00:07:43,617
It's possible.

115
00:07:43,618 --> 00:07:45,317
If that is true,

116
00:07:45,318 --> 00:07:48,517
then it will answer Mitsuhiko's questions.

117
00:07:48,518 --> 00:07:49,917
Oh, please!

118
00:07:49,918 --> 00:07:52,017
Don't you remember?

119
00:07:52,018 --> 00:07:55,717
The robber jumped off the building opposite here

120
00:07:55,718 --> 00:07:58,317
