127
00:08:21,618 --> 00:08:22,817
Triathlon!

128
00:08:22,818 --> 00:08:23,918
What?

129
00:08:25,418 --> 00:08:29,317
If you're still into that iron man race,

130
00:08:29,318 --> 00:08:31,118
