131
00:08:33,218 --> 00:08:35,717
Is that you, Conan?

132
00:08:35,718 --> 00:08:38,618
I was wondering where you were.

133
00:08:39,718 --> 00:08:41,517
Now, where are you, Conan?

134
00:08:41,518 --> 00:08:43,517
I'm in the building opposite!

135
00:08:43,518 --> 00:08:45,318
The robber jumped off, right?

136
00:08:46,518 --> 00:08:48,717
Now I'm going up the stairs to the roof where the robber jumped off!

137
00:08:48,718 --> 00:08:50,517
There's something I wanted to try.

138
00:08:50,518 --> 00:08:53,217
So I told them to throw the questions until I'm ready!

139
00:08:53,218 --> 00:08:55,518
What is it, then?

140
00:09:05,818 --> 00:09:08,018
Can you see me from there?

141
00:09:13,618 --> 00:09:15,517
Yeah, I can see you.

142
00:09:15,518 --> 00:09:17,617
But what are you exactly trying to do?

143
00:09:17,618 --> 00:09:19,517
Hey, don't you remember?

144
00:09:19,518 --> 00:09:23,817
I mean, about what the lady living right above that house said.

145
00:09:23,818 --> 00:09:24,818
She woke up in 2 am midnight

146
00:09:24,819 --> 00:09:27,617
