149
00:09:35,718 --> 00:09:37,617
I think I got the mystery behind it,

150
00:09:37,618 --> 00:09:40,017
and now I'm going to show that to you all!

151
00:09:40,018 --> 00:09:41,517
Conan?

152
00:09:41,518 --> 00:09:43,017
Okay, that's enough!

153
00:09:43,018 --> 00:09:45,617
I'm helping you guys because it's my former staff

154
00:09:45,618 --> 00:09:47,817
