155
00:09:47,818 --> 00:09:51,517
It looks like these kids really want me to be the robber.

156
00:09:51,518 --> 00:09:53,517
But it's only kid's shallow cleverness after all.

157
00:09:53,518 --> 00:09:56,218
I can't believe you're actually listening to them!

158
00:09:57,518 --> 00:09:59,517
Again, like I said,

159
00:09:59,518 --> 00:10:00,917
if I was the robber,

160
00:10:00,918 --> 00:10:03,817
