00:15:21,181 --> 00:15:24,580
after being chased by a police officer!

251
00:15:24,581 --> 00:15:26,380
You got that right! Also, when he jumped off,

252
00:15:26,381 --> 00:15:28,180
he dropped the bag with the jewelries

